msgid ""
"**Improved** `Istio CNI </docs/setup/additional-setup/cni/>`_ robustness."
" Previously, when a node restarted, new pods may be created before the "
"CNI was setup, causing pods to be created without ``iptables`` rules "
"configured (`Issue 14327 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/14327>`_)."
msgstr ""

